From: Sumit Garg <sumit.garg@linaro.org>
Date: Wed, 16 Oct 2019 10:44:55 +0530
Subject: KEYS: trusted: Move TPM2 trusted keys code
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc1
Git-commit: 2e19e10131a08dc65079c755fb6e8af936bfedbd
References: jsc#SLE-15209

Move TPM2 trusted keys code to trusted keys subsystem. The reason
being it's better to consolidate all the trusted keys code to a single
location so that it can be maintained sanely.

Also, utilize existing tpm_send() exported API which wraps the internal
tpm_transmit_cmd() API.

